name: Dip Eye Liner - Black
description:
Our Liquid Dip Liner - a true-black, waterproof masterpiece. Our highly pigmented formula effortlessly glides on, ensuring flawless and precise lines. From sharp, thin lines to bold, dramatic strokes, this liner never skips or smudges, providing you with unrivaled control and confidence.




Ingredients: Aqua (Water), Ammonium Acrylates/Acrylonitrogens Copolymer, Propylene Glycol, Polysorbate 20, Tocopheryl Acetate (Vitamin E), Phenoxyethanol, Methylparaben, Ethylparaben, Propylparaben, Iron Oxide Black (CI 77499)
